names.bio: Tara Strong was born on February 12, 1973 in Toronto, Ontario, Canada as Tara Lyn Charendoff. She is an actress, known for My Little Pony: Friendship Is Magic (2010), The Fairly OddParents (2001) and The Powerpuff Girls (1998). She has been married to Craig Strong since May 14, 2000. They have two children.
